OL,3,CWales' environmental regulator is
OL,4,C'missing in action' as ex-employees
OL,5,Cspeak out
OL,7,FNatural Resources Wales (NRW) is an
OL,8,Fenvironmental regulator responsible
OL,9,Ffor protecting the environment and
OL,10,Ftackling climate change. In 2023, its
OL,11,Fbudget from the Welsh Government was
OL,12,F#145million.
OL,14,FSpeaking for the first time with S4C's
OL,15,Fcurrent affairs flagship programme Y
OL,16,FByd ar Bedwar, Dr Wiik says she felt
OL,17,Fshe was "wasting" her "life's purpose"
OL,18,Fat the organisation.
