OL,3,CWales' environmental regulator is
OL,4,C'missing in action' as ex-employees
OL,5,Cspeak out
OL,7,FNRW say that real progress has been
OL,8,Fmade in improving the quality of
OL,9,Fwater, land and air over the last 30
OL,10,Fyears.
OL,12,F'No point being there'
OL,14,FDr Wiik, originally from Finland,
OL,15,Fchose to work for NRW's climate change
OL,16,Fand then rivers unit because she
OL,17,F"loves nature and wants to make a
OL,18,Fdifference".
OL,20,FBut she says she soon realised there
OL,21,Fwere issues within the organisation.
