OL,3,CWales' environmental regulator is
OL,4,C'missing in action' as ex-employees
OL,5,Cspeak out
OL,7,F"I just realised how things just
OL,8,Fdidn't work, how things were at a
OL,9,Fstandstill, there weren't enough
OL,10,Fresources, and it was very, very
OL,11,Fdifficult," she said.
OL,13,F"It was the most insane level of
OL,14,Fbureaucracy I've ever come across."
OL,16,FDr Wiik said she felt there was "no
OL,17,Fpoint being there" (at NRW) after she
OL,18,Fbecame more and more frustrated with
OL,19,Fthe organisation.
