OL,3,CWales' environmental regulator is
OL,4,C'missing in action' as ex-employees
OL,5,Cspeak out
OL,7,FDuring her employment, she says she
OL,8,Funcovered internal documents in which
OL,9,FNRW admitted multiple failings
OL,10,Fincluding an acknowledgement that 80%
OL,11,Fof permitted discharge permits were
OL,12,Fnot being monitored.
OL,14,FDr Wiik also raised concerns about
OL,15,Fmonitoring of nature, which is among
OL,16,FNatural Resources Wales' statutory
OL,17,Fobligations. While researching the
OL,18,Fcondition of Welsh rivers, she said
OL,19,Fshe was surprised to learn that some
OL,20,Fof the most recent data available for
OL,21,Fher to access dated back to 2007.
