OL,5,Cspeak out
OL,7,FProblems on the ground
OL,9,FThe programme also hears from Andrew
OL,10,FThomas, from West Wales Rivers Trust,
OL,11,Fwho is frustrated with NRW's response
OL,12,Fto pollution incidents.
OL,14,FWhile sympathetic with the public
OL,15,Fbody's staff, Mr Thomas said he has
OL,16,Freported at least 10 instances of
OL,17,Fpollution over the last few months,
OL,18,Fbut is "lucky" if these are attended
OL,19,Fon the same day.
