OL,3,CWales' environmental regulator is
OL,4,C'missing in action' as ex-employees
OL,5,Cspeak out
OL,7,F"They're missing in action - it breaks
OL,8,Fmy heart," he said.
OL,10,FResearch by Y Byd ar Bedwar found that
OL,11,FNatural Resources Wales did not attend
OL,12,Fmore than half of incidents reported
OL,13,Fto them between January 2023 and
OL,14,FJanuary 2024.
OL,16,FOn one occasion, a report of water
OL,17,Fpollution in the River Teifi in west
OL,18,FWales was not attended for 118 days.
