OL,3,CWales' environmental regulator is
OL,4,C'missing in action' as ex-employees
OL,5,Cspeak out
OL,7,FMr Thomas said: "You can talk and
OL,8,Ftalk, but when someone is polluting
OL,9,Fthrough the winter, and through the
OL,10,Fsummer, and nothing happens, well,
OL,11,Fnothing is going to change."
OL,13,FNRW respond
OL,15,FClare Pillman, the chief executive of
OL,16,FNatural Resources Wales, rejected a
OL,17,Frequest for an interview on Y Byd ar
OL,18,FBedwar, but said in a statement that
OL,19,Freal progress has been made in
OL,20,Fimproving the quality of water, land
OL,21,Fand air over the last 30 years.
