OL,5,Cspeak out
OL,7,F'Do not shy from enforcement'
OL,9,FShe added: "We are also strengthening
OL,10,Fthe way we regulate to drive better
OL,11,Fperformances from across the wider
OL,12,Fagricultural, industrial and water
OL,13,Fsectors. This includes introducing
OL,14,Fspecialist officers on the ground,
OL,15,Fincreasing compliance checks and using
OL,16,Fnew data and intelligence tools to
OL,17,Finform our work. We are also seeking
OL,18,Fadditional powers to consider civil
OL,19,Fsanctions for a broader range of
OL,20,Fenvironmental offences.
