OL,3,CWales' environmental regulator is
OL,4,C'missing in action' as ex-employees
OL,5,Cspeak out
OL,7,F"But like all public bodies, our
OL,8,Fresources are finite and we have to
OL,9,Fmake informed decisions about how and
OL,10,Fwhere to focus our efforts to protect
OL,11,Flives, livelihoods and the
OL,12,Fenvironment. While we will continue to
OL,13,Fbe astute and innovative in how we use
OL,14,Fthe resources we do have, we will need
OL,15,Fto prioritise those actions to ensure
OL,16,Fthey have the best outcomes for people
OL,17,Fand for nature, and that they deliver
OL,18,Fthe improvements to our environment
OL,19,Fthat we all want to see."
