OL,7,FConcerns about NRW were presented to
OL,8,Fthe Welsh Government, who are
OL,9,Fresponsible for funding the
OL,10,Forganisation.
OL,12,FHuw Irranca-Davies MS, the cabinet
OL,13,Fsecretary for climate change and rural
OL,14,Faffairs acknowledged that "NRW is
OL,15,Fstretched".
