OL,3,CWales' environmental regulator is
OL,4,C'missing in action' as ex-employees
OL,5,Cspeak out
OL,7,FHe said the Welsh Government has given
OL,8,F"an additional #18m" to the
OL,9,Forganisation in order to "deliver
OL,10,Ftheir statutory and regulatory
OL,11,Ffunctions", and acknowledged that NRW
OL,12,Fwanted to "lift standards up across a
OL,13,Fwide range of issues that they deal
OL,14,Fwith".
OL,16,FBut he said there was pressure on the
OL,17,Fentire public sector, and "if there
OL,18,Fwas an ideal world and we would've
OL,19,Fbeen able to invest more in it, I
OL,20,Fwould have done it".
