OL,7,FAndrew RT Davies MS, leader of the
OL,8,FWelsh Conservatives in the Senedd,
OL,9,Fsaid: "These testimonies are just the
OL,10,Ftip of the iceberg. NRW is not fit for
OL,11,Fpurpose, it needs to be scrapped and
OL,12,Freplaced."
